title: Battlefield of the Mind: Winning the Battle in Your Mind
description:
Joyce Meyer, "Battlefield of the Mind: Winning the Battle in Your Mind"
English | ISBN: 0446691097 | 2002 | 288 pages | PDF | 3,7 MB

In celebration of selling 3 million copies, FaithWords is publishing a special updated edition of Battlefield of the Mind. Worry, doubt, confusion, depression, anger and feelings of condemnation: all these are attacks on the mind.

If readers suffer from negative thoughts, they can take heart! Joyce Meyer has helped millions win these all-important battles. In her most popular bestseller ever, the beloved author and minister shows readers how to change their lives by changing their minds.
